  return "user reading history and behavioral patterns, subscription and payment information, personalization preferences and followed topics, saved articles and bookmarks, push notification tokens and delivery preferences, account credentials and session tokens, location data for regional content, advertising identifiers and consent records, audio/video playback history, offline cached content, newsletter subscription data, and reader engagement analytics";
